  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[Always reduce the rank by 1]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[Change the eigenvalues]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
</question>
<!-- Q7 --><question type="multichoice">
  <name><text>Rank - Parametric Family</text></name>
  <questiontext format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p>For which value of \(k\) does \(A=\begin{pmatrix}1&2&k\\3&6&9\end{pmatrix}\) have rank 1?</p>]]></text></questiontext>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Answer: (C) \(k=3\)</strong></p><p>Row 2 = 3×Row 1 requires \(9=3k\), i.e., \(k=3\). Then rank = 1. If \(k\neq3\), row 2 is not a multiple of row 1, and rank = 2.</p>]]></text></generalfeedback>
