<!-- Q11 --><question type="multichoice">
  <name><text>Rank - Consistency of Linear System</text></name>
  <questiontext format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p>The system \(Ax=b\) is consistent (has a solution) if and only if:</p>]]></text></questiontext>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Answer: (B) \(\mathrm{rank}(A)=\mathrm{rank}([A|b])\)</strong></p><p>Rouché–Capelli theorem: \(Ax=b\) has a solution iff \(b\) is in the column space of \(A\), which happens iff the augmented matrix \([A|b]\) has the same rank as \(A\). If consistent, the solution is unique iff nullity\((A)=0\), i.e., rank\((A)=n\) (number of variables).</p>]]></text></generalfeedback>
  <defaultgrade>1.0</defaultgrade><penalty>0.25</penalty><hidden>0</hidden>
  <single>true</single><shuffleanswers>true</shuffleanswers><answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\det(A)\neq0\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="100" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A)=\mathrm{rank}([A\mid b])\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(b=0\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(A\) is symmetric]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
</question>
<!-- Q12 --><question type="multichoice">
  <name><text>Rank - rank(A+B) inequality</text></name>
  <questiontext format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p>For matrices \(A\) and \(B\) of the same size, which inequality always holds?</p>]]></text></questiontext>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Answer: (A) \(\mathrm{rank}(A+B)\leq\mathrm{rank}(A)+\mathrm{rank}(B)\)</strong></p><p>Sub-additivity of rank: the column space of \(A+B\) is contained in the sum of column spaces of \(A\) and \(B\). So rank\((A+B)\leq\) rank\((A)+\)rank\((B)\). The reverse can fail drastically: \(A=-B\) gives rank\((A+B)=0\).</p>]]></text></generalfeedback>
  <defaultgrade>1.0</defaultgrade><penalty>0.25</penalty><hidden>0</hidden>
  <single>true</single><shuffleanswers>true</shuffleanswers><answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
  <answer fraction="100" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A+B)\leq\mathrm{rank}(A)+\mathrm{rank}(B)\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A+B)\geq\mathrm{rank}(A)+\mathrm{rank}(B)\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A+B)=\mathrm{rank}(A)\cdot\mathrm{rank}(B)\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A+B)=|\mathrm{rank}(A)-\mathrm{rank}(B)|\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
</question>
