<!-- Q14 --><question type="multichoice">
  <name><text>Rank - Rank One Update</text></name>
  <questiontext format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p>If \(A\) is invertible and \(u,v\in\mathbb{R}^n\), then by the Sherman–Morrison formula, \(A+uv^T\) is invertible unless:</p>]]></text></questiontext>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Answer: (B) \(v^TA^{-1}u=-1\)</strong></p><p>Sherman–Morrison: \((A+uv^T)^{-1}=A^{-1}-\frac{A^{-1}uv^TA^{-1}}{1+v^TA^{-1}u}\), valid when \(1+v^TA^{-1}u\neq0\). When \(v^TA^{-1}u=-1\), the denominator is 0, meaning \(A+uv^T\) is singular (rank drops by 1). This formula is used in optimization and quasi-Newton methods.</p>]]></text></generalfeedback>
  <defaultgrade>1.0</defaultgrade><penalty>0.25</penalty><hidden>0</hidden>
  <single>true</single><shuffleanswers>true</shuffleanswers><answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(u=v\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="100" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(v^TA^{-1}u=-1\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\|u\|=\|v\|=1\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(u^Tv=0\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
</question>
<!-- Q15 --><question type="multichoice">
  <name><text>Rank - Normal Matrix Rank</text></name>
  <questiontext format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p>\(\mathrm{rank}(A^TA)=\) ?</p>]]></text></questiontext>
  <generalfeedback format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Answer: (C) \(\mathrm{rank}(A)\)</strong></p><p>The null spaces of \(A\) and \(A^TA\) are equal: \(A^TAx=0\Leftrightarrow x^TA^TAx=0\Leftrightarrow\|Ax\|^2=0\Leftrightarrow Ax=0\). By rank–nullity, rank\((A^TA)=n-\)nullity\((A^TA)=n-\)nullity\((A)=\)rank\((A)\). Similarly rank\((AA^T)=\)rank\((A)\).</p>]]></text></generalfeedback>
  <defaultgrade>1.0</defaultgrade><penalty>0.25</penalty><hidden>0</hidden>
  <single>true</single><shuffleanswers>true</shuffleanswers><answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A)^2\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(2\,\mathrm{rank}(A)\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="100" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A)\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
  <answer fraction="0" format="html"><text><![CDATA[\(\mathrm{rank}(A)-1\)]]></text><feedback format="html"><text></text></feedback></answer>
